  ('dietitian-moex-03564', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-101-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關硒之吸收與代謝的敘述，何者正確？', '["攝取量高時，多餘的硒由糞便中排除", "攝取無機型態的亞硒酸鹽（selenite），吸收率低於10%", "硒營養狀況理想者，小腸之吸收率很低", "吸收率可達50%~100%，過量攝取會中毒"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:31:02+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f6ff4eb0312d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a8c8b3621973", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "101030", "c": "107", "s": "0602", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "營養學", "year": "101", "exam_name": "101年第一次專技醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師藥師醫事檢驗師護理師護士社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
